&lt;p&gt;Some heaters are watches.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(I) Some heaters are projectors.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(II) Some lamps are heaters.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(III) All watches are lamps&lt;/p&gt;

